I fought a lvl 41 wiz friend of mine recently.  I used a fire pet thinking this would allow me to outdamage him thats a big NO.  He rooted the pet stunned me and it was all downhill from there.  Next fight i made an earth pet gave him weapons but did NOT cast burnout 2 on him there is no point.  I then used malaise on my friend.  The earth elemental kept him rooted in place and although he rooted my pet he could not get away and was thus interrupted frequently for the duel i used my shock of spikes as it is faster and doesnt check fire or ice resists.  Just my 2 cents I am lvl 40 btw
