First off i must say it usually does not matter what pet you use against wizards, air is the best however.  They should all die quickly, if they root your pet, then he is dead unless he resists your DD, if he doesnt root your pet, then he is VERY dead.  and yes we can kill tank classes with ease.  Monks and rogues are simple, earth best obviously is the best but not necessary.  make sure you malise them so the pet root sticks most of the time, then relax and nuke, very simple.  <P>Myddraal<BR>40th MAge of Erud<BR>Solusek Ro<BR>Bloodstone Templar<BR>Magic House
