<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Duel starts with the wizard having the mage's pet targeted.<P>Wizard yonders (shadow step) the hell out of casting reach. shadow Step is 1 second casting time so he would cast it off before you or your pet could do a thing. Besides, its almost mana free.<P>Wizards walks step by step towards the mage casting root on pet (it was targeted remember?) till he is within casting range and hence landing root on mage's pet.<P>Good luck on a petless nuking battle against a wizard   <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>If root wears off, reapply proces, but by the time root wears off or mage dispells it with cancel magic, mage would be most likely dead.<P>--------------------<P>Yaguex, warlock, Paradigm, Solusek Ro.
