one thing most people tend to miss out on about our pets when it comes to fighting against mages and wizards (pvp or npcs) the fire pet has uber resistance to fire, which eliminates 85% of mages nukes, and probably half of the wizzies vs the pet.. this worked sooo much better for me then air pet vs. cynthia at lvl 29-31 when i got bored with her.<P>against players the effect would be less noticable cuz most peoplewould realize after one or two resists that they need to stop using fire spells.. of course a lot of pvpers probably won't bother killing your pet knowing it'll die when you do.
